         </image>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="/Users/user/Documents/dev/python/DITA/topics-dita/209969577-How-do-I-design-a-secure-app-.dita" xtrc="p:34;317:10">You'll see below how the slice ensured Justin A. Sample
    would only be able to view his own past assignments.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="/Users/user/Documents/dev/python/DITA/topics-dita/209969577-How-do-I-design-a-secure-app-.dita" xtrc="p:35;319:10">

